sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI
    participant Generator as TGMCTSElitesGenerator
    participant Mission as MissionPlanMixin
    participant MCTS
    participant Validator as ValidationMixin
    participant Store as PersistenceMixin
    participant Simulator as Aerialist/PX4
    participant Scoring as ScoringMixin
    participant Archive as MAP-Elites
    participant Plotter as PlottingMixin
    participant Confirm as ConfirmationMixin
    participant Selector as SelectionMixin

    User->>CLI: generate case-study.yaml budget
    CLI->>Generator: construct(case-study)
    CLI->>Generator: generate(budget)
    Generator->>Mission: parse YAML and referenced .plan
    Mission->>Mission: evaluate eight frame mappings
    Mission-->>Generator: local reference path
    Generator->>Store: create or resume mission-aware run
    Store-->>Generator: restored results, history, confirmations, pending candidate

    loop exploration while attempt limit remains
        Generator->>MCTS: tree_policy(root)
        MCTS-->>Generator: candidate node
        Generator->>Validator: validate candidate input
        alt invalid before simulator
            Validator-->>Generator: validation reasons
            Generator->>Store: log invalid candidate
        else valid candidate
            Validator-->>Generator: input compliant
            Generator->>Store: persist pending candidate
            Generator->>Store: consume simulator attempt
            Generator->>Simulator: execute test
            alt system error
                Simulator-->>Generator: exception
                Generator->>Store: log system error
                opt retry allowed and budget remains
                    Generator->>Simulator: rerun same pending scenario
                end
            else evaluated execution
                Simulator-->>Generator: trajectory, distances, ULG
                Generator->>Scoring: point, reward, mission outcome, failure evidence
                Scoring-->>Generator: EvalResult
                alt official distance failure
                    Generator->>Store: save YAML, ULG, overview, XY-time
                else safe, near miss, or non-official non-completion
                    Generator->>Store: keep metadata only
                end
                Generator->>Archive: update elite cell
                Generator->>MCTS: backpropagate reward
                Generator->>Store: append result and history
                opt snapshot interval reached
                    Generator->>Plotter: save history, tree, and progress plots
                end
            end
        end
    end

    opt confirmation reserve and candidate failures
        Generator->>Confirm: confirm top failures
        loop remaining confirmation attempts
            Confirm->>Store: consume attempt
            Confirm->>Simulator: rerun same obstacle scenario
            Simulator-->>Confirm: observed result
            alt reproduced official distance failure
                Confirm->>Store: save confirmation failure artifacts
            else not reproduced
                Confirm->>Store: retain metadata only
            end
            Confirm->>Store: append confirmation observation
        end
    end

    opt unused total budget remains
        Generator->>MCTS: return remaining budget to exploration
    end

    Generator->>Selector: final_suite()
    Selector->>Selector: allow completed or not_completed official failures
    Selector->>Selector: reject unknown completion
    Selector->>Selector: robust quality ranking
    Selector->>Selector: geometry and trajectory-DTW diversity
    Selector-->>Generator: selected tests
    Generator->>Plotter: save final history, tree, and progress plots
    Generator-->>CLI: selected tests and run id
    CLI->>Generator: export best_ranked_failed_tests
    CLI->>CLI: export generated_tests with same run id
    CLI-->>User: print selected count and output paths
